title: OsuExchange
subtitle: [Github](https://github.com/alittlerocket/osuExchange)
description: A **API wrapper** for the ```osu!``` API for **Python**. Allows easy access to statistics and data from ```osu!``` through easy to use **Python** commands. Supports both puplic endpoints, and endpoints that require **authentification** through a simple user token. **Downloadable on pip.**
